: 8d08:main:main:                       rust: 2 (0x2)\nrt: 8d08:main:main:                       rust: 8 (0x8)\nrt: 8d08:main:main:                       rust: 2048 (0x800)\n```\n\nThe shift-left `0u << b` is necessary to make this happen, but `0u >> b` and `0u >>> b` suffice to reproduce the bug just as well.  Also, changing `b <<= 1u` to `b = b << 1u` makes the bug go away.\n", "closed_by": null, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/152/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/152/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": "completed"}